window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Gavin Gregory often stares into the abyss - that's his job. An elite profiler at the FBI's Behavioral Analysis Unit, he hunts serial killers for a living. He knows how they behave, how they think, what motivates them. Considered the best at what he does, Gavin goes to investigate when it appears a dormant psychopath has reactivated. The case takes a bizarre turn when psychiatrist Debra Esteves contacts him and says she knows who the enigmatic killer is.</p> <p>It soon becomes apparent that what she means is that she knows what the killer is.</p> <p>But Gavin is a man of science, a rational man. Can she keep him safe from what is hunting him long enough to convince him she's right?</p>"; 
